title: GoPro: Breakdance in Beijing
description:
A group of friends scout around the 798 Art District of Beijing, in search of an ideal spot for a B-Boy session.

Shot 100% on the HERO4® & HERO4® Session camera

Music
Afrolicious "Bring it to the Max"
Additional Music Courtesy of ExtremeMusic
